NormalFlashTime.description: How long the Rings flash at a normal speed, before they begin flashing quickly.

QuickFlashTime.description: How long the Rings flash quickly before disappearing.

NormalFlashSpan.description: How long the delay is in-between flashes while rings are flashing at a normal speed.

QuickFlashSpan.description: How long the delay is in-between flashes while rings are flashing quickly

Rings.description: Moon Rings controlled by this manager.
